The Top 20 Most Popular
Performance Appraisal Software



Performance Appraisal software is a subset of talent management software that streamlines the employee review cycle. This software helps managers assess the work of their employees accurately and objectively, and make important decisions about promotions and firings. Below is a look at the most popular options as measured by a combination of their total number of clients, active users and online presence. In order to see a comprehensive list, please visit our Performance Appraisal Software Directory. 












